| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2168 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 91cc9176-e303-5049-8e3b-92d6486ae2ab"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
